sec.p:
Total RNA extracted from dissected medial cortices of E14.5 embryonic brains was reverse transcribed by Superscript III reverse transcriptase (Invitrogen). Quantitative PCR was performed on an Applied Biosystems 7900 quantitative PCR instrument using SYBR green. Transcript levels were normalized to the expression levels of Gapdh. Primer sequences are as follows:
Ascl1 F: CATCTCCCCCAACTACTCCA; Ascl1 R: CCAGCAGCTCTTGTTCCTCT;
Dlx2 F: AGCTACGACCTGGGCTACAC; Dlx2 R: TGGCTTCCCGTTCACTATTC;
Gapdh F: CGTCCCGTAGACAAAATGGT; Gapdh R: GAATTTGCCGTGAGTGGAGT.
